data.title: PCP Network List Oct.02
data.meta_description: PCP_Network_List_Oct.02.xlsx - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document lists various private clinics and pharmacies located in Abu Dhabi (AUH) and Ajman (AJM), along with their provider codes. In AUH, there are over 50 listed clinics and over 50 pharmacies. In AJM, there are over 30 listed clinics and over 50 pharmacies. The clinics and pharmacies are all privately operated healthcare providers in these two cities.
